        "info": "## OpenAPI TLS Test Flow\n\nThis flow is used for e2e testing of OpenAPI/HTTPS functionality.\n\n### Test Endpoints\n\n| Method | Path | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| GET | /health | Health check endpoint |\n| GET | /openapi.json | OpenAPI specification |\n| GET | /docs | Swagger UI |\n\n### TLS Configuration\n\nThis flow requires certificates generated by mkcert:\n- Server certificate: tests/e2e/certs/server.crt\n- Server key: tests/e2e/certs/server.key\n- CA root: tests/e2e/certs/rootCA.pem"
